        <title type="html"><![CDATA[R语言下载和安装教程]]></title>
        <id>https://Super-dong94.github.io/post/R 语言下载和安装教程/</id>
        <link href="https://Super-dong94.github.io/post/R 语言下载和安装教程/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-06-01T16:17:12.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h6 id=""></h6>
<h4 id="font-colorred软件fontfont-color008b8b介绍font"><font color='red'>软件</font><font color='#008B8B'>介绍</font></h4>
<p>R是用于统计分析、绘图的语言和操作环境。R是属于GNU系统的一个自由、免费、源代码开放的软件，它是一个用于统计计算和统计制图的优秀工具。</p>
<h4 id="font-colorred软件fontfont-color008b8b下载font"><font color='red'>软件</font><font color='#008B8B'>下载</font></h4>
<p>[测试环境]：Windows 10 64 bit （32 bit也可以安装）</p>
<p>[版  本  号]：R-4.1.0 （该软件截止发文，为最新版本）</p>
<p>[下载链接]：公众号内回复： <strong><font color='#008B8B'>RStudio</font></strong> ，最好复制一下，不然错了没有回复的</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210602002849695.png" alt="image-20210602002849695" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h4 id="font-colorred软件fontfont-color008b8b安装font"><font color='red'>软件</font><font color='#008B8B'>安装</font></h4>
<p>1.双击R软件</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083122080.png" alt="image-20210528083122080" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>2.点击运行</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083146897.png" alt="image-20210528083146897" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>3.点击确定，继续安装</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083210963.png" alt="image-20210528083210963" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>4.点击下一步</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083241376.png" alt="image-20210528083241376" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>5.选择安装文件夹（ <strong><font color='#008B8B'>路径中不能含有空格、中文字符</font></strong> ）</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083314724.png" alt="image-20210528083314724" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>6.点击下一步</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083422645.png" alt="image-20210528083422645" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>7.点击下一步</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083510867.png" alt="image-20210528083510867" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>8.下一步</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083532278.png" alt="image-20210528083532278" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>9.直接点下一步（之后使用R studio，所以不需要R的快捷方式）</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083554049.png" alt="image-20210528083554049" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>10.正在安装</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083642007.png" alt="image-20210528083642007" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>11.安装成功</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083730167.png" alt="image-20210528083730167" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>12.我们可以从程序栏打开看看界面，就这样简单粗糙的界面</p>
<p><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528083811398.png" alt="image-20210528083811398" loading="lazy">13. <strong><font color='#008B8B'>R语言安装完成后，需要安装R studio，所以，接下来应该看R studio的安装教程</font></strong> ，继续关注吧！</p>
]]></content>
